name: Reologica Instruments
overview:
REOLOGICA Instruments AB is a new concept company. Its mission is to provide leading edge instrumentation, customized service and application support to instrumentation users. It is a Swedish company situated close to the University of Lund in the southern part of Sweden. Quality, reliability and simplicity are the strict engineers goals for all products. The REOLOGICA Instruments staff has many years experience in instrument development, application knowledge and instrument service.

REOLOGICA Instruments has gained full international confidence and have a qualified distribution network covering the main markets throughout the world. All products are supported by a full range of service, application laboratory, training courses, seminars and network support for customer service and consultation. This reflects the commitment to provide products, service and consultation to give you the best value for your investment. Only the best is good enough for all our customers. They deliver instruments of high guarantied quality.

funding_rounds.source_description: Svenska Generationsskiften are investing in Reologica
